This APK contains the latest version of the YouTube Translator app with the following improvements:

1. Completely redesigned URL input field using Material Design components:
   - Replaced simple EditText with TextInputLayout and TextInputEditText
   - Added better error handling with inline error messages
   - Implemented auto-focus on app start and clear text button
   - Made keyboard appear automatically when starting the app

2. Enhanced video playback with ExoPlayer
3. On-device English to Russian translation using ML Kit
4. Clean, modern user interface

To install:
1. Download this APK to your Android device
2. Enable "Install from Unknown Sources" in your device settings
3. Open the downloaded APK file to install the app
4. Launch the app and enter a YouTube URL

Note: This is the latest version as of March 27, 2025.
